EmailTemplate.name: MSF Bloomberg Confirm Access
EmailTemplate.subject: [Case#{!Case.CaseNumber}] Your Access to Markit Securities Finance's data on Bloomberg
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
You now have access to IHS Markit Securities Finance's short interest data on Bloomberg.
Attached with this email are the following documents which you may find useful:
1. FAQ Document 2. Data Dictionary 3. Cheat Sheet
To find the data, please type SI <GO> and click the tab titled “Markit Securities Finance – Daily”.
If you require any further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us.
Kind regards, {!Case.OwnerFullName} IHS Markit | Customer Care
